{
  "stem": "24958.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were not only alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were maybe a hundred people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When we were standing there in the snow, we didn't know, so we decided to walk.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We walked, and we walked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we saw some lights.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We knew that some people must live there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we knocked on the door, a few houses, and they-- they took us in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were nice people, good people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we spent the night there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the next day, we-- we tried to go to some train station, and we went back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you never knew why--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and we never knew where we were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We found out-- we found out wherever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember the name of it, a small town somewhere about four or five hours away from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they took us together, about a hundred people, they took all of their homes in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they transported us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think they did something which they're not supposed to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think they let us go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're not supposed to do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, some flee.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some went back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't-- I had a little boy with me, four years old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What would-- where should I go?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we tried to go back, or we went back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not too long, not too long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we went back to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we-- we came in the ghetto in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then-- then we--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the train.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went on our own.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went on our own.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't-- we had to go there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were signs and things that said, all Jews have to move there-- there-- there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they gave us a room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They gave us-- I couldn't go to my apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
